#: buildVars.py:17
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Provides enhanced terminal accessibility for Windows Terminal and "
"PowerShell, enabling screen reader users to efficiently navigate and "
"interact with command-line interfaces. Inspired by TDSR (Terminal Data "
"Structure Reader) and incorporates functionality from both TDSR and Speakup."
" Advanced features inspired by community suggestions and discussions."
msgstr ""
"Proporciona accesibilidad de terminal mejorada para Windows Terminal y "
"PowerShell, lo que permite a los usuarios de lectores de pantalla navegar e "
"interactuar de manera eficiente con interfaces de línea de comandos. "
"Inspirado en TDSR (Terminal Data Structure Reader) e incorpora funcionalidad"
" tanto de TDSR como de Speakup. Funciones avanzadas inspiradas en "
"sugerencias y debates de la comunidad."

#: buildVars.py:14
